<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="M.C3.A9moire_politique_:_Dominique_Richard.2C_ex-d.C3.A9put.C3.A9"><a href="/wiki/Memoire_politique" title="Memoire politique" class="mw-redirect">Mémoire politique</a>&#160;: Dominique Richard, <font style="background:red">ex-député</font></span></h2>
<div class="floatright"><a href="/wiki/File:DominiqueRichard.jpg" class="image" title="Dominique Richard"><img alt="Dominique Richard" src="/wiki/images/1/1c/DominiqueRichard.jpg" width="150" height="192" /></a></div>
